---

<div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 lg:px-0">
  <section class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-12 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
				Hi! I'm Noel. Software designer and developer.
      </h1>

      <p class="font-thin text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed">
				I help climate nonprofit and startup leaders turn ideas into working software —from concept to launch and beyond.
      </p>

      <p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body-subtle leading-relaxed">
				My expertise combines a design background with 20 years of software engineering experience. I build web apps like maps, knowledge bases, wizards and databases.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <div class="md:sticky md:top-8">
        <img
          src="/img/noel-landscape-768.jpg"
          alt="Portrait of Noel"
          class="w-full max-w-md h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg md:hidden"
        />
        <img
          src="/img/noel-portrait-500.jpg"
          alt="Portrait of Noel"
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg hidden md:block"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-12 py-12 md:py-16 border-t border-gray-200 ">
    <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-heading tracking-tight">
				Here's the problem
      </h2>

      <p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 ">
				Web and software projects are risky and overwhelming
      </p>

      <ul class="font-thin space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 ">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Wrong estimates and bugs lead to project delays and cost overruns.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Developers use jargon instead of language that's relevant to your domain.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Endless coordination meetings needed to align stakeholders and service providers.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>Your vision gets watered down as it passes between teams.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>You discover costly technical issues only after design is &quot;<em>done</em>.&quot;</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
		</div>
    <div class="md:col-span-2 hidden md:block">
      <img
        src="https://placehold.co/400x400/e2e8f0/64748b?text=Image"
        alt="Image placeholder"
				class="w-full max-w-sm h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
			/>
    </div>
  </section>

	<section class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-12 py-12 md:py-16 border-t border-gray-200 ">
		<div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-heading tracking-tight">
				There is a better way
			</h2>

			<p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600">
				Guaranteed results, handled by a single expert
			</p>

			<ul class="font-thin space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 ">
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>You'll know exactly what to expect in terms of quality, cost and time.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Conversations happen in a language that is natural to you and your organization. </span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>You get a thought partner that helps you align goals, stakeholders and priorities.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Your vision stays intact, with one person ensuring that every design and implementation detail aligns with it.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Strategic decisions draw on both design insight and technical foresight.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600">
				You'll never have to explain a runaway cost or product flop to your stakeholders or board.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="md:col-span-2 hidden md:block">
			<img
				src="https://placehold.co/400x400/e2e8f0/64748b?text=Image"
				alt="Image placeholder"
				class="w-full max-w-sm h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
			/>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-12 md:py-16 border-t border-gray-200 ">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
			<h2 class="text-orange text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
				How is this possible?
			</h2>

			<p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 ">
				Clear requirements, small steps, and solid experience
			</p>

			<ul class="font-thin space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 ">
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span><strong>Thorough discovery and requirements definition.</strong> We settle on success criteria only when we have a shared understanding of your goals and how the project helps you move towards them.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span><strong>We break large projects into manageable milestones.</strong> I work on milestones with fixed price and defined with clear success criteria. I keep going until the project meets the criteria —regardless of effort required. To cover unexpected issues, I offer a bug-free guarantee.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span><strong>You don't pay by the hour; you pay for results.</strong> When you pay developers by the hour, there's no incentive to get things done fast and without bugs. With fixed-price milestones, I'm incentivized to deliver efficiently while maintaining quality.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span><strong>I’ve been doing this for 20 years.</strong> That’s why I can bear the risk of offering guarantees —which I have been providing for years.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-12 md:py-16">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto rounded-lg border border-c02 p-6 md:p-8 shadow-lg">
			<p class="text-c06 md:text-lg mb-4">
				We have been working with Noel for over three years. He's communicative, responsive and a great developer.
			</p>

			<p class="font-thin text-c06 md:text-lg mb-4">
				Noel developed a fit-for-purpose platform that has allowed us to build and maintain our tools relatively independently despite having very little technical expertise. He's helped us expand the platform, think about how to better serve our users, and find ways to improve it.
			</p>

			<p class="font-thin text-c06 text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-green">
				— Maria Lucien. Program Associate, People Powered
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-12 md:py-16">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto rounded-lg border bg-white/50 border-c04 p-6 md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-c06">
				Let's work together?
			</h2>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700  mb-4">
				Schedule a 30-minute exploratory call to discuss your project and determine if we're a good match.
			</p>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700  mb-4">
				You'll get clarity on your project's feasibility, potential approaches, and realistic next steps. I'll answer your questions directly based on 20 years of experience.
			</p>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700  mb-6">
				If working together makes sense, I'll follow up with a proposal.
			</p>

			<a href="#" class="inline-block bg-orange hover:bg-orange/75 transition-colors text-ground font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
				Schedule now
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-12 md:py-16 border-t border-gray-200 ">
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-4">
			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 ">
				Not ready to schedule? Explore some of my work
			</p>
			<a href="/portfolio/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 md:text-lg hover:underline">
				<span>Portfolio</span>
				<img src="https://placehold.co/24x24/3b82f6/ffffff?text=→" alt="" class="w-6 h-6" />
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</div>
